{"580133":{"detail":{"date":"2026-04-06","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/55/50/580133_4AttU.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/55/50/580133_4AttU.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/55/50/580133_4AttU.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/55/50/580133_4AttU.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/55/50/580133_4AttU.jpg"},"summary":"突然届けられた1億円と謎の招待状\r\n\r\n女子大生のカンザキナオは、嘘と駆け引きで巨額のマネーを奪い合う\r\n「ライアーゲーム」に突如として巻き込まれてしまう。\r\n他人を疑うことを知らない「バカ正直」のナオは、開始早々、絶体絶命の窮地に陥る。\r\n\r\nそんな彼女が頼ったのは、詐欺罪で服役し、釈放されたばかりの男・アキヤマシンイチ。\r\n鋭い洞察力と圧倒的な知略を持つ「元天才詐欺師」・アキヤマと共に、\r\nナオは異常なゲームの只中へと足を踏み入れていく。\r\n\r\n嘘つきだらけの世界で、正直者は何を見るのか。\r\n\r\n人間の本質を抉る、\r\n究極の心理ゲームが今、開幕する！","name":"LIAR GAME","name_cn":"欺诈游戏","tags":[{"name":"2026年4月","count":253,"total_cont":0},{"name":"智斗","count":204,"total_cont":0},{"name":"MADHouse","count":203,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫画改","count":203,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":160,"total_cont":0},{"name":"推理","count":150,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2026","count":134,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫改","count":92,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":73,"total_cont":0},{"name":"青年向","count":52,"total_cont":0},{"name":"川野麻美","count":38,"total_cont":0},{"name":"大逃杀","count":22,"total_cont":0},{"name":"佐藤雄三","count":20,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2026年","count":16,"total_cont":0},{"name":"浦畑達彦","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"悬疑","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TVA","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本动画","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"未上映","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"小泉纪介","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"4","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"MADHOUSE[疯房子]","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日画","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"表","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"都市日常","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"解说","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TVA-02","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"春夏半年番","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧情","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"三话弃","cou